Package: STEAM
Type: Package
Title: Significance Threshold Estimation for Admixture Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kelsey Grinde
Maintainer: Kelsey Grinde <kgrinde@macalester.edu>
Description: Estimate genome-wide significance thresholds for admixture
    mapping studies. For more information about the methods, see our paper 
    published in 2019 in the American Journal of Human Genetics: Grinde et 
    al., "Genome-wide significance thresholds for admixture mapping studies".
